node.text:
An Xbox employee made it their mission to save a gamer's Xbox 360 profile picture following its slow and painful demise 👇

Gabriel Roland took to Twitter to show how the Xbox software was shrinking his avatar every generation and it piqued the interest of Eden Marie, engineering lead at Xbox.

After some hard work, Marie did it! She fixed the avatar and now the software changes to bring this update to everyone seems to be in its alpha stages. 💚🎮
